X GND 4 0 -600 100 U 50 50 1 1 W
X AREF/PB0 5 600 300 100 L 50 50 1 1 T
X PB1 6 600 200 100 L 50 50 1 1 T
X PB2 7 600 100 100 L 50 50 1 1 T
X VCC 8 0 600 100 D 50 50 1 1 W
ENDDRAW
ENDDEF
